general.gigTitle: develop or create a wix website redesign for your business

sellerCard.oneLiner: Wix Legend Partner And Squarespace Circle Member
sellerCard.description: Greetings, I am a seasoned UI/UX designer and Website developer with over 7 years of industry experience. Having completed 300+ projects across various sectors, I offer a comprehensive solution for website design, updates, and SEO services. Let's connect to discuss how I can contribute to your project's success.

description.content:
Hello, Warm welcome to my Gig !


I take pride in providing user centered experiences so whether you need a website for your any type of Business, Non-Profit, eCommerce or whatever you can dream up I'm here to help. 


This listing is for a fully custom website quick turn-around design on the WIX platform. As I have been awarded a LEGEND badge by Wix which is the TOP ranked Wix Partner Award and I am in there Official Partner Program.


I don't use Wix Pre-Built Templates as I will work on your wix website according to your requirements.


Service Includes:


  • High-quality & unmatched wix website design.
  • Redesign your wix website and take it to the next level.
  • Fully responsive on mobile, tablet & laptop.
  • Follow the style of another site you like.
  • Copy your Figma design to Wix.
  • Add the Latest Features
  • Payment Gateway Integration
  • Online Booking Features
  • And Much More!!


Also included:


  • 14 days of Free Support.
  • Premium High Quality Images FREE.
  • Domain Configuration.
  • On-time Delivery.
  • Social Media Integration.
  • Full Refund Policy.


Please contact me before placing order so that we discuss important details it will improve the Quality of the Project!


Thank you for your interest!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Why choose Wix ahead of wordpress?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Unlike WordPress, which often requires third-party plugins for e-commerce functionality, and Shopify, which has a monthly subscription fee, Wix offers an all-in-one platform. With Wix, you get hosting, domain registration, website builder, and e-commerce capabilities all in a single package.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What are the necessary requirements that i have to provide ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: For Your WIX website , we need your website Logo, your pages names and their contents, social media link if you have , Your business detail , pictures (if you don`t have i will provide you Some Free picture related to your website )

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is it necessary to purchase the WIX PREMIUM ACCOUNT before to order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, You can purchase it later, If you want to connect your domain name with Wix account than you need to purchase the Wix premium account but you can do it later.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is Wix free to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, Wix is 100% free to start a stunning website. you can upgrade to premium at any time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you Negotiate in prices?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: yeah, I am always ready to negotiate to fit your budget. I will make sure you will get expected product in the reasonable price. Please INBOX ME to negotiate on prices

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you provide a free support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will be providing 14 days wix technical support. So, You can get me here any time.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you be offering SEO services for wix?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yeah, I will be offering Wix website Seo services.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What about Multi-Language Website?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Contact me for a quote and custom offer. You will need to deliver text for each language. Please note that if the language contains specific characters, font choice will be limited. If you don't have the text I will arrange it for you at very reasonable cost.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What is like to have a Wix website ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Wix is Very user friendly , you can use its professional features and edit your website after it is designed by us with zero knowledge , just upload and edit anything as usual , or we will guide you with our Note

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you help me out if I did not know how to edit website.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide a tutorial on how you will be able to edit yourself.
